channel.title: New Autoer Idea =)
channel.description:
Hey guys, im new to this forum, and was sent here by friday(From fgf) to say a new idea, and considering there isnt an appropriate forum for this, ill post it here. Anyways, on to the idea.
Well, i was thinking that we could use Wpe (packet sniffer/tracer thingy) To record packets sent by actions (i.eGod strikes, that are annoying to click) and send the packets at a faster speed, Im not sure if this would work, but if it does, We could have Some AWSOME xp ;D
